WEBVTT

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:02.376
on cancer research than on Alzheimer's

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:05.440
despite the fact
that Alzheimer's costs us more

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:10.720
and causes a similar number
of deaths each year as cancer.

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:15.616
The lack of resources
stems from a more fundamental cause:

00:03:15.640 --> 00:03:17.000
a lack of awareness.

00:03:18.600 --> 00:03:22.000
Because here's what few people know
but everyone should:

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:27.640
Alzheimer's is a disease,
and we can cure it.

